task.summary: > Equilibrium RectBispline on psi rectegular grid now. > O-points and X-points are identified. > Components of poloidal magnetic field are computed (only on R,Z grid for now) > Added simple test file loading some basic equilibria.

add: support of adding mapped flux functions - for testing (!). add: setting smoothing of spline smoothing factor in constructor add: pressure and f-function profile added to equilibrium add: calculation of toroidal field
add: io package with function for loading Fiesta g-file equilibria.
add: testing plot of monkey patched functions.
add: limiter support for fiesta files
Data with sample limiter added. Example test file done more readable. Extended skeleton of Coordinates class
normalized poloidal flux is from now markerd as psi_n added testing function matisek's readeqdsk
fix: increased quality of finding extremes now it should be fine even in plasmas with coils add: testing_utils file with function to load simple some testing equilibrium
